[src:sbom/dependency-hell] By examining the source, the functionality can be rewritten in a much more compact way (with respect to the license).
[src:sbom/dependency-hell] In general, this can significantly reduce the application code, reduce later maintenance costs, and improve the software writing skills of programmers.
[src:sbom/dependency-hell] The major version only changes when programs that used that version will no longer be compatible.
[src:sbom/dependency-hell] The minor version might change with even a simple revision that does not prevent other software from working with it.
